description: The push/pull/legs split is a simple training method. You split your body into three parts and each part is trained on a seperate day.
A pushing workout that targets your upper chest and shoulders.
Press the bar from your chest until your arms are close to locking and repeat.

Press the bar vertically from your upper chest.
